nodes.text: Gus Treta was the outermost of the three moons of the planet Corellia. It was orbited by the Gus Treta Inner-System Market Station, which circled the moon five times a day.
In Star Wars Galaxies, three moons could be viewed from the surface of Corellia, as well as from space. One of these moons must have been Gus Treta.
